# ─── App ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development

# Extra hostnames allowed to reach the app (comma-separated). localhost /
# 127.0.0.1 / [::1] always work; add a LAN IP or mDNS name here if you open
# Loop Studio from another device. Anything else is rejected with 403.
# LOOP_ALLOWED_HOSTS=192.168.1.20,mymac.local

# ─── Loop Studio (AI chat) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional: server-side Anthropic key so the Loop Studio chat replies live
# in-app without each user pasting their own key. When unset (and the user has
# not saved a key in the AI Team Manager), chat falls back to the IDE bridge.
# A per-user key (Anthropic sk-ant-… or Google AI Studio AIza…) wins over these.
# Provider is auto-detected from the key prefix.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza... or AQ....  # free tier via Google AI Studio (aistudio.google.com)
# LOOP_GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash   # optional: override the Gemini model
